&lt;h1 id="views-and-spaces"&gt;Views and Spaces&lt;a class="anchor" href="#views-and-spaces"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let&amp;rsquo;s say we have a simple problem: we want to run a vector add and we want to run it on the GPU. We may start with a code that looks like this:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>